    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@vinhlh Thanks for opening this issue.\r\n\r\nWe took this approach so one could do:\r\n\r\n```jsx\r\nconst AwesomeRefinementList = connectRefinementList(AwesomeRefinementListComponent);\r\n\r\n<AwesomeRefinementList attributeName=\"brands\" />\r\n<AwesomeRefinementList attributeName=\"materials\" />\r\n```\r\n\r\nAnd this actually works, if it does not then we failed somewhere, open a bug.\r\n\r\ninstead of\r\n\r\n```jsx\r\nconst Brands = connectRefinementList(AwesomeRefinementListComponent, {attributeName: 'brands'});\r\nconst Materials = connectRefinementList(AwesomeRefinementListComponent, {attributeName: 'materials'});\r\n\r\n<Brands />\r\n<Materials />\r\n```\r\n\r\nBut if you like it, you could just do:\r\n\r\n```jsx\r\nconst AwesomeRefinementList = connectRefinementList(AwesomeRefinementListComponent);\r\nconst Brands = <AwesomeRefinementList attributeName=\"brands\" />;\r\nconst Materials = <AwesomeRefinementList attributeName=\"materials\" />;\r\n\r\n<Brands />\r\n<Materials />\r\n```\r\n\r\nIs you proposal bringing or coming from anything else than syntax preference?",
